    <item>
      <title>移民正在推动美国经济增长，而政客们却愤怒不已</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/immigration-is-fueling-us-economic-growth-while-politicians-rage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管美国移民数量的增加在全国政治家之间播下了分歧的种子——并激起了一大群选民的焦虑——在一个地方，几乎每个人似乎都在同一个乐观的页面上：华尔街。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/immigration-is-fueling-us-economic-growth-while-politicians-rage</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 10:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佩尔茨获得支持，迪士尼董事会之争演变成一场竞赛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/disney-board-fight-turns-into-a-contest-as-peltz-gathers-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在带领华特迪士尼公司度过了历史上最严重的衰退之一后，首席执行官鲍勃·艾格(Bob Iger)看起来已经准备好与亿万富翁活动家纳尔逊·佩尔茨(Nelson Peltz)争夺董事会席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/disney-board-fight-turns-into-a-contest-as-peltz-gathers-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度停止向俄罗斯供应受制裁油轮巨头的石油</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/india-stops-taking-russian-oil-delivered-on-sovcomflot-tankers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国的制裁，所有印度炼油厂现在都拒绝接收 PJSC Sovcomflot 油轮上运载的俄罗斯原油，这使得自两年前入侵乌克兰以来蓬勃发展的贸易进一步复杂化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/india-stops-taking-russian-oil-delivered-on-sovcomflot-tankers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 08:53:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市有望实现 2012 年以来最长涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/european-stocks-on-track-for-longest-winning-run-since-2012</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市周五基本持平，守住历史高位，并有望连续第九周上涨，这是自 2012 年以来最长的连续上涨，原因是人们对经济的信心不断增强，而且降息即将到来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/european-stocks-on-track-for-longest-winning-run-since-2012</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 08:23:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走强抵消基本面紧缩影响，油价稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走强抑制了投资者对大宗商品的兴趣，抵消了全球原油市场趋紧的迹象，伦敦油价稳定在每桶 85 美元上方。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-22</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 23:22:43 GMT</pubDate>
